      1pm – 2pm = Children&rsquo;s (7-13) competition<br />
      2pm-3pm = Women&rsquo;s competition<br />
      3pm-4pm = Men&rsquo;s competition </p>
    <p>Sunday 10am – 11:30am = practice throws<br />
      1:30 = Children&rsquo;s (7-13) competition<br />
